WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:14.628 --> 00:00:15.840
Where are you off to

00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:17.840
Out !

00:00:24.297 --> 00:00:26.297
You didn't even have your lunch

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:11.607
Hey

00:01:12.089 --> 00:01:13.377
How are you ?

00:01:14.152 --> 00:01:16.152
Fine, I guess

00:01:20.173 --> 00:01:22.173
What is going on with you

00:01:22.822 --> 00:01:27.184
Nothing, wait, I hate them

00:01:27.653 --> 00:01:29.150
Who ?

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.318
My parents, they don't give us any freedom

00:01:34.787 --> 00:01:39.478
Well, do you want to do something fun ?

00:01:42.476 --> 00:01:43.680
Is that

00:01:44.204 --> 00:01:45.827
Cillian that app is dangerous

00:01:45.827 --> 00:01:49.860
Yup yup but, it is the dare for you app

00:01:50.168 --> 00:01:52.168
I always wanted to try it

00:01:54.439 --> 00:01:58.576
So we press this button and it gives us a challenge

00:01:58.827 --> 00:02:00.827
Exactly

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:04.651
And whatever challenge it gives we have to do it for points ?

00:02:04.882 --> 00:02:06.882
You are correct

00:02:07.072 --> 00:02:09.072
So easy

00:02:09.914 --> 00:02:12.605
Look, even famous people are doing it

00:02:13.046 --> 00:02:16.974
Hi Greta Thornton here, I am trying out Dare for you app

00:02:21.512 --> 00:02:23.456
Now it is raining badly

00:02:23.842 --> 00:02:26.324
Well, if they can do it so can we

00:02:42.104 --> 00:02:44.104
The statue ?

00:02:46.044 --> 00:02:47.415
Record

00:02:48.506 --> 00:02:50.506
No, no, Hannah !

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:12.462
What are you doing ?

00:03:13.300 --> 00:03:15.300
Cillian, run !

00:04:18.778 --> 00:04:20.778
Don't pick it up

00:04:21.637 --> 00:04:23.637
I wasn't going to

00:04:30.329 --> 00:04:32.329
Hannah, are you going to do this

00:04:33.001 --> 00:04:35.001
Oh I will do it !

00:05:18.517 --> 00:05:21.900
Hannah, I am going to try this one

00:05:22.357 --> 00:05:25.866
Seriously, you can't Cillian it is too dangerous

00:05:26.088 --> 00:05:27.732
Get lost !

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:39.600
Is she in town ?

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:41.600
I think so

00:07:13.584 --> 00:07:15.584
What about this one ?

00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:19.660
Jesus Christ

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:32.554
Are you sure it is safe

00:08:32.874 --> 00:08:35.168
We will find out

00:09:12.221 --> 00:09:15.290
Cillian, she cannot swim

